subject: we're dangerously close

Click here to watch our latest ad. [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/loc_q42024_mcf-tvad4?amount=&amounts;=,,,,] 📺 From doctors explaining the terrible consequences of the abortion ban, to real Missourians sharing their stories on why an abortion was the right decision for them – these ads are influential. But right now, we're dangerously close to having to pull them off the air… We're less than 3 days from the election, so slowing down right now could be the difference between ending the total abortion ban, or allowing anti-abortion politicians to continue restricting our freedoms. Is there anything you can spare to help us renew our TV ads? We need $15,000 in the next 24 hours in order to meet the renewal deadline.
